description: This project will enable Federated states of Micronesia (FSM) to prepare its Second National Communication (SNC) to the Conference of the Parties of the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC).

subproject.description: Through the project, FSM will prepare a National Communication comprising three major elements: a national greenhouse gas inventory, abatement analysis, and vulnerability and adaptation assessments. The project will assist FSM meet its reporting obligations to the UNFCCC.
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
